name: A make-believe to save us all
description:
if it gets you by 
why not
but please
spare me
your gods
the one, two and three

I don't mind your make-believe
I hope it saves us all
and if it doesn't 
I would still get by
with my make-believe

the one two cha cha cha

( I didn't have a description for this, so wrote up these words, if it makes sense to you, embrace it..if it doesn't ignore it :)
